    "Therefore, we totally treat 16 datasets, i.e., 4 datasets with one regular and three irregular settings, and 11 baselines.• Stock [6]: The Google stock dataset was collected irregularly from 2004 to 2019.",
    "Each observation has (volume, high, low, opening, closing, adjusted closing prices), and these features are correlated.• Energy [37]: This dataset is from the UCI machine learning repository for predicting the energy use of appliances from highly correlated variables such as house temperature and humidity conditions.",
    "• Air [38]: The UCI Air Quality dataset was collected from 2004 to 2005.",
    "Hourly averaged air quality records are gathered using gas sensor devices in an Italian city.",
    "• AI4I [39]: AI4I means the UCI AI4I 2020 Predictive Maintenance dataset."
